  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of this prospective randomized study is to assess the safety and efficacy of
      video-assisted lung segmentectomy (Group B) comparing with mini muscle-sparing thoracotomy
      (group A) during diagnostic process for pulmonary nodules.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
